**Example**:-
we have to convert {a,c,e,g,i|b,d,f,h,j} ---> {a,b,c,d,e|f,g,h,i,j}

step-1: {a,c,e,g,i|b,d,f,h,j}
Encode using **num = (const * a) + b** for n to 2*n-1 indices of array

step-2: {a,c,e,g,i|(a+b),(c+d),(e+f),(g+h),(i+j)}
Decode a & b as-
**a = num/const
b = num%const**

